Title: remove user
As a... admin
I want to... remove a user from the system
So that... the active user list stays up to date when someone leaves

Acceptance criteria:

Admin can remove a normal user from the system
Removed user no longer appears in the user list
A normal user cannot remove another user
The active user list stays up to date after a user is removed

Acceptance Test:

Test 1: Admin removes a normal user
Given: admin exists in the system
And: exampleuser exists in the system
And: exampleuser appears in the active user list
When: admin removes exampleuser
Then: exampleuser is no longer in the system
And: admin deletion succeeds
And: exampleuser no longer appears in the active user list

Test 2: Normal user cannot remove another user
Given: otheruser exists in the system
And: exampleuser exists in the system
And: exampleuser appears in the active user list
When: otheruser tries to remove exampleuser
Then: exampleuser is still in the system
And: deletion is denied
And: exampleuser still appears in the active user list

Test 3: User list is updated after removal
Given: admin exists in the system
And: exampleuser exists in the system
And: the active user list contains admin and exampleuser
When: admin removes exampleuser
Then: the active user list no longer contains exampleuser
And: the active user list still contains admin